attributes.background:
The Reindeer Liberation Front, by dint of many years hard work and undercover investigation, have exposed cruel and unethical treatment of reindeer by the semi-deity, Santa Claus (also known in the English-speaking world as Father Christmas, Old St Nick or Kris Kringle)

Our long-standing campaign has featured in the media overseas in places as diverse as Germany, Canada and Japan.

The RLF would now like the UK Government to take a stand on:-
the uninspected working and living conditions of the animals; 
lack of proper training and veterinary qualifications among the deer-handlers and other staff;
concerns about the safety of such a large vehicle travelling through international airspace without proper Air Traffic Control monitoring and clearances;
repeated landings in residential areas;
and, not least of all, 
widespread reports that Mr Claus frequently drives his team whilst under the influence of alcohol.
